*Danish: [[circus]]
*French: [[cirque]] ''m''
*Italian: [[circo]] ''m''
*Japanese: [[サーカス]], [[曲馬団]], [[曲芸]]
*Portuguese: [[circo]] (1), [[cruzamento]] (2)
*Romanian: [[cerc]]
*Sardinian: [[circu]], [[tzircu]]

